1306:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/pbuf.c ****  * Creates a single pbuf out of a queue of pbufs.
1307:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/pbuf.c ****  *
1308:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/pbuf.c ****  * @remark: Either the source pbuf 'p' is freed by this function or the original
1309:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/pbuf.c ****  *          pbuf 'p' is returned, therefore the caller has to check the result!
1310:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/pbuf.c ****  *
1311:Middlewares/Third_Party/LwIP/src/core/pbuf.c ****  * @param p the source pbuf
